\b\f0\fs22\insrsid1927860 kaum \lquote Ad (QS. Hud: 50),}{\rtlch \af0\afs22 \ltrch \f0\fs22\insrsid1927860  Nabi Shalih diutus untuk kaum }{\rtlch \ab\af0\afs22 \ltrch \b\f0\fs22\insrsid1927860 Tsamud (QS. Hud: 61)}{\rtlch \af0\afs22 \ltrch 
